{
  "stem": "16571.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we are-- now, when someone is ill or somebody dies, we all rush to hospitals.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We all rush to see them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We all rush.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I feel it like-- also I feel bad, and I felt bad about losing my wife.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I feel almost as bad when this, recently, only two weeks ago, a very good friend of mine, Frank [?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Farkash, ?] died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then a week before that, another friend of mine, Manny, Manny Barnard died.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then we had Bernard, Bernard [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Dreihorn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, and there is one or two who are still ill.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it makes you feel-- the phone goes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Suddenly, everybody rings everybody to say, oh, by the way, he is in hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that's the hospital.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it-- it's-- it's-- it's like I'm losing my own flesh and blood.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because we were brought up since we were 14, 15, 16.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We came over here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were like that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[POINTS] No, I can't explain it to you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That is a bond between us no other people in the world have, not even in Israel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "In Israel, they're spread out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There's lots of survivors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There was lots of survivors there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they-- they-- they don't even like talking about it because they brought their own problems with the wars and all that stuff.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But here, we are immune from what they've got in Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we feel more attached to one another.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it's-- it's just-- it's terrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It's just terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, lately, twice before I went to simcha, the phone goes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Steve, there is a levaya tomorrow-- twice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's just-- it's just-- it's just 13.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We used to-- we used to make an evening and worry, who can we leave out?",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
